"""Test get_disk_technology_pool_stats."""
response = self.perf.get_disk_technology_pool_stats(disk_tech_id=self.
    p_data.disk_technology, metrics=pc.KPI, start_time=self.time_now,
    end_time=self.time_now)
self.assertIsInstance(response, dict)
self.assertEqual(response.get('reporting_level'), self.common.
    convert_to_snake_case(pc.DISK_TECH_POOL))
